Federation:
-----------
- Users outside AWS get temporary role
- Fed can have many flavours:
 > SAML 2.0
   - Integrate on prem AD with AWS
   - Need to setup a trust between AWS IAM and SAML
   - SAML 2.0 enables web-based, cross domain SSO
   - Uses STS api AssumeRoleWithSAML
   - Now use amazon SSO
 > Custom Identity Broker
   - More work 
 > Web identity Federation with Amazon Cognito
   - Create IAM role with Cognito
   - Build trust between OIDC IDP and AWS 
   - Support anonymous users
   - Supprot fo MFA
   - Data Sync

 > Web identity Fed without cognito
 > SSO
 > Non-saml with AWS MS AD
- Using Fed, user managment is done outside AWS


